overview: Head back to 2007 and watch how Kayfabe Commentaries revolutionized the shoot-style interview genre with the premiere edition of YouShoot!  We asked you, the public, to send us your video files and emailed questions that The Honky Tonk Man would have to answer on-camera, in front of the world. And you were told, as is the heart of the YouShoot series, to ask ANYTHING.  It’s over two hours of outrageousness as one of pro wrestling’s most outspoken personalities is put on the hotseat – forced to answer exactly what the people want…  …whether or not they want to hear it!
title: YouShoot: Honky Tonk Man
